---
title: Roman Chicken with Mashed Potatoes
description: Juicy chicken is nestled in a delicious tomato and bell pepper sauce. It’s a perfect weeknight dish that’s super quick and easy, but also exceptionally delicious. To soak up all that sauce, we’ve served it over creamy mashed potatoes, but it goes equally well over pasta or even rice.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54d21ed36ced6e6f1b8b4568.jpg
